---
import DocsLayout from '../../components/docs/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout
  title="Getting Started — Preview | NozzleNote by BMR"
  description="Getting started with the NozzleNote by BMR documentation preview."
  eyebrow="Documentation preview"
  heading="Getting started preview."
  intro="NozzleNote by BMR is in development, so this guide is an early documentation preview rather than final product instructions."
>
  <section class="docs-section" aria-labelledby="overview-title">
    <h2 id="overview-title">Current direction</h2>
    <ul class="plain-list">
      <li>No public download is available yet.</li>
      <li>Start by understanding the intended product scope: printer profiles, maintenance history, preventive prompts, parts notes, and local-first records.</li>
      <li>Use the roadmap and release preparation page for current status.</li>

    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="content-panel" aria-labelledby="status-title">
    <span class="status-pill">Preview</span>
    <h2 id="status-title">Not final release documentation.</h2>
    <p>Public app screenshots, final workflows, downloads, paid plans, verified catalogs, account features, and support desk procedures are not available yet.</p>
  </section>
</DocsLayout>
